    "english": "The Supplication of the Lenient Supporter.\r\n\r\nThis magnificent supplication is reported from the Holy Prophet, peace be upon him and his Household. It was revealed to him while he was offering a prayer in Maqam Ibrahim (the Standing-place of Prophet Abraham). In his two books of al-Balad al-Amin and al-Misbah, al-Kaf’ami has mentioned this supplication and referred to its innumerable merits as a footnote. Among these merits is that if this supplication is said in the white days4 of the holy month of Ramadan, sins will be forgiven even if they are as many as rain drops, leaves of trees, and sands in wastelands. It is advisably said for healing diseases, settling one’s debts, saving from poverty, relieving grief, and releasing from adversities:\r\n\r\nIn the name of Allah, the Beneficent, the Merciful Glory be to You. O Allah! Exalted are You. O Beneficent! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Merciful! Exalted are You. O Generous! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Sovereign! Exalted are You. O Master! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Holy! Exalted are You. O Peace! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Source of security! Exalted are You. O Loving Protector! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Glorious! Exalted are You. O Omnipotent! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Proud! Exalted are You. O Dominant Helper! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Creator! Exalted are You. O Maker! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Fashioner! Exalted are You. O Pre-ordainer! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Guide! Exalted are You. O Ever-Living! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Liberal! Exalted are You. O to Whom return all repentant! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Liberator! Exalted are You. O Comforter! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Chief! Exalted are You. O Liege-Lord! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Near! Exalted are You. O Preserver! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Originator! Exalted are You. O Resurrector! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Praiseworthy! Exalted are You. O Glorified! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Eternal! Exalted are You. O Mighty! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Very Forgiving! Exalted are You. O Appreciator! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Ever-present! Exalted are You. O Witness! Succor us from the fire,. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Compassionate! Exalted are You. O Kind! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Causer! Exalted are You. O Lord-possessor! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Vivifying! Exalted are You. O Annihilator! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Loving! 'Exalted are You. O Helping Friend! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Companion! Exalted are You. O Familiar! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Magnificent! Exalted are You. O Elegant! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O All-knowing! Exalted are You. O All-seeing! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Benevolent! Exalted are You. O Possessor of fortune! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Adored! Exalted are You. O Ever-Existing! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Forgiver! Exalted are You. O Subduer! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to You. O Rememberable! Exalted are You. O Thankworthy! Succor us from the fire. O Giver of succor! Glory be to